snippet.title: MySims Kingdom DS HD Gameplay (MelonDS)
snippet.description:
MySims Kingdom DS HD Gameplay (MelonDS)
Release Date: October 28, 2008
Platforms: Wii, Nintendo DS

Info: MySims Kingdom is a video game developed by EA Redwood Shores and published by Electronic Arts as a spin-off to Maxis' The Sims franchise for the Nintendo DS and Wii in 2008.
_____________________________________________
Graphics Card: GeForce RTX 2060
CPU: AMD Ryzen 5 2600 Overclocked to 3.9 GHz
Ram: Corsair Vengeance 32 GB DDR4 3200Mhz
Motherboard: MSI B450 Tomahawk
SSD: Samsung 860 EVO 500GB
OS: Windows 10
Emulator Version: Latest one as of upload date.
_____________________________________________
If you enjoyed this video, make sure to leave a like and let me know in the comments which games you'd like to see me play next. Thanks for watching!
